{"word":"ἀλινδέω","slug":"ἀλινδέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλινδέω</b></el> <p/><i>to make to roll</i> (but <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> only occurs in <a href='S:composition'>compos.</a> with <el>ἐξ</el>):— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to roll in the dust</i> (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>ἀλινδήθρα</el>):— <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to roam about</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/>"}]}